CommentBody:
@John Hilsher We believe that the customer has something in their environment  that is modifying users and we cannot see these changes because the customer is not licensed for AD activity.

If you can issue an RTU for Activity Monitor – Active Directory Activity support can deploy activity monitor to quickly identify who, what and when deletions are happening.

John will work to get the key generated for an RTU for Activity Monitor - Active Directory Activity for today's (19Sept) customer meeting.
